title: Cambridge Analytica files for U.S. bankruptcy
text:
Cambridge Analytica files for U.S. bankruptcy 11:37am BST - 01:19
Cambridge Analytica, the firm at the center of a data misuse scandal that's engulfed Facebook, has filed for bankruptcy in the U.S. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
